channel.title: Error code in Eclipse Console?
channel.description:
Hi there - this also occurs in the server run window:
[07/06/14 22:42]: [Stage - 1] Launching Project Insanity - Evolved... [07/06/14 22:42]: [Stage - 2] Done Loading Object Configuration. [07/06/14 22:43]: [Stage - 3] Done Loading Region Configurations [07/06/14 22:43]: Exception in thread "Thread-1" [07/06/14 22:43]: java.lang.Error: Unresolved compilation problem: The method run() of type EventManager must override a superclass method
[07/06/14 22:43]: at engine.event.EventManager.run(EventManager.java:84) [07/06/14 22:43]: at java.lang.Thread.run(Unknown Source) [07/06/14 22:43]: [Stage - 4] Loaded: 1023 Doors in: 408ms. [07/06/14 22:43]: [Stage - 5] Loaded: 273 Double Doors in: 169ms. [07/06/14 22:43]: [Stage - 6] Server Connected to 0.0.0.0:43594 [07/06/14 22:48]: Average Cycle Time: 0ms [07/06/14 22:48]: Players online: 0, engine load: 0.0%
I'm sorry if this is a nooby question, but I'm fairly new to this and I'm not entirely sure what to change to get it to work! I'm guessing this is why I can't connect to the server with my client...
Thanks
